se.jguru.nazgul.core.xmlbinding.api

Class DefaultNamespacePrefixResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.jguru.nazgul.core.xmlbinding.api.DefaultNamespacePrefixResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NamespacePrefixResolver

    public class DefaultNamespacePrefixResolver
extends Object
implements NamespacePrefixResolver
    Default POJO implementation of the NamespacePrefixResolver specification, relating unique XML namespace URIs to unique XML prefixes. Implemented for runtime lookup speed rather than minimal memory footprint.
    Author:
    Lennart Jörelid, jGuru Europe AB
    See Also:
    NamespacePrefixResolver
